        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>If he were on the commission, he would want to focus more on education and conversation, because “statue or not,” he says, “the fact that the conversation is even sparked is acknowledgement.”</p>
<p><em>Alicia Sun is a Trinity senior. Her column typically runs on alternate Thursdays.&nbsp;</em></p>

